titles.title: Kakawatte wa Ikenai Type no Musume ga Kanojo ni Natta
Dating the Kind of Girl You Shouldn't Get Involved With
関わってはいけないタイプの娘が彼女になった

title: Kakawatte wa Ikenai Type no Musume ga Kanojo ni Natta
title_japanese: 関わってはいけないタイプの娘が彼女になった
title_synonyms: Dating the Kind of Girl You Shouldn't Get Involved With
synopsis:
The female protagonist, Miyu, is your typical gold-digger girl—she hooks up with guys, milks them for all they're worth, then dumps them and moves on to her next prey. Yuuki-kun, her latest target, seems to just be your typical nice guy that genuinely looks out for Miyu, completely oblivious of her intentions. However, something's different about him that makes Miyu unable to carry on her usual scheme...

(Source: MangaDex)
background: Kakawatte wa Ikenai Type no Musume ga Kanojo ni Natta is a web manga released on the author's Twitter and pixiv accounts from June 10, 2022, to July 21, 2023, and published in print by Kadokawa on October 23, 2023. The series has been published as doujinshi from December 31, 2022, to December 31, 2023, when the volumes were released at Comic Market 101, 102, and 103, respectively.
